                        <interp inst="t18420228-name-708" type="given" value="HENRY"></interp>HENRY BRAND</persName>
                  </hi>. I was at the public-house that night—I lodge there—the prisoner was there.</p>
               <p>
                  <hi rend="italic">Cross-examined. Q.</hi> You did not see any thing done with the shawl?</p>
               <p>
                  <hi rend="italic">A.</hi> No.</p>
