               <p>
                  <hi rend="italic">Cross-examined. Q.</hi> You saw him walking along Castle-street? <hi rend="italic">A.</hi> Yes, about 150 yards from the public-house, which is in Mercer-street—I asked what he had in his pocket—he said, "A shawl and a cap"—I asked him where he got them—he said he picked them up in Mercer-street. (The prisoner received a good character.)</p>
